Class ArraySplitter<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • permafrost.tundra.lang.ArraySplitter<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The component type of the array.

    public class ArraySplitter<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Encapsulates splitting a given array into a head and tail.
